{"title":"apache_markdown","type":"markdown","aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"## 租屋網 Apache Log 重要欄位解析
1. client ip: 組屋網用戶IP
2. agent: 用戶登錄媒介
3. geoip.country_name: 用戶IP顯示地址
4. http_method: 用戶行為
* [HTTP Request](https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods)
5. request: 用戶目標
6. response: 用戶得到的反饋
* 6.1 資訊回應 (Informational responses, `100`–`199`)
* 6.2 成功回應 (Successful responses, `200`–`299`)
* 6.3 重定向 (Redirects, `300`–`399`)
* 6.4 用戶端錯誤 (Client errors, `400`–`499`)
* 6.5 伺服器端錯誤 (Server errors, `500`–`599`)
7. byte: 用戶使用流量
8. referer: 網址來源"}}
